oads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.ynwmmv1lhumb-jpg.webp 720w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.ynwmmv1lhumb-300x169.webp 300w" width="720" height="405" /></a></p><p>来自加拿大VTuber办公室“Phase <a href="https://twitter.com/PhaseConnectJP" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Connect</a> ”的组合“Phase KALEiDO”的成员将于1月27日星期六和1月28日星期日举行首次发行。</p><p>成员为<a href="https://twitter.com/kaminariclara_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kurara Kaminari</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/grampico_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Piko Kuramu</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/kannagiloki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Giroki Kanna</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/ayaseyuu_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">、</a> Yu Ayase、 <a href="https://twitter.com/kokoromomemory" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Memori Koi</a> ，“Kokoromomemori”共有5人。</p><p>涩谷十字路口5号屏幕将于1月22日（周一）9:00至1月28日（周一）23:35期间发布“Phase KALEiDO”出道纪念视频广告。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【出道预告】VTuber经纪公司“Phase Connect”登陆日本！ ！ ！ [相万花筒]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ioe0npY81ps?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000002.000135981.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Phase Connect Ltd 新闻稿</a></p><h2>STARDUST支持的“虚拟明星试镜vol.1”举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.kjz1303sfwhy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.kjz1303sfwhy-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.kjz1303sfwhy-jpg.webp 720w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1431a04188a5d5b6dfd1dbb88f0f15b5-kix.kjz1303sfwhy-300x157.