board-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMmSnJrK-R_bjFpMpdAS_Jg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>亚马米（Yamamami）</strong></a>上传了一件像万圣节一样的作品，充满了艾亚卡西（Ayakashi）飞行的活泼，骚乱和乐趣。这首歌是<a href="https://twitter.com/ayass4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ayamama Ayame</a>举办的活动“ Scream Garden”的主题歌曲，这是一款黑暗而有趣的MV，其中包括活动人员，一个黑暗的氏族。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-1024x574.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-1024x574.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-768x430.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.gbv64l8vhrnb-jpg.webp 1253w" width="1024" height="574" /></a></p><p>弹跳的低音和节奏的用法以及Yamami的棘手声音同时令人兴奋，同时聆听和激动。似乎唱歌的困难似乎很高，因为根据这一部分所需的技能，Yamamami用所有这些技术唱歌。好像他们带领鬼魂自由飞行。<br />将来，尖叫的花园活动之一也将是这首歌的<a href="https://twitter.com/ayass4/status/1745779243924304197" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VR歌手冠军</a>，我期待看到一位歌手如何唱歌非常困难的歌曲。</p><h2> [原创MV]“家庭故事/亨伯特·亨伯特”[Kagura Mea / Yugorobel] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[原创MV]“家庭故事/亨伯特·亨伯特”[Kagura Mea / Yugorobel]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kh1vGzU6HH4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@YukokuRoberu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>夜晚</strong></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@KaguraMea" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>之后，卡古拉·毛拉（Kagura Maura</strong></a> ）的合作“ Robel no Tomea”上传了“同一故事”封面。唱着潮湿信任的歌曲具有很高的歌唱能力的两个人正在仔细唱歌，并使其变得美丽。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-1024x572.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-1024x572.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-768x429.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/741b5acf56dc1843afe6f2abb9eb2775-kix.nzyq9nk9vj6h-jpg.webp 1254w" width="1024" height="572" /></a></p><p>最初，“ Robel Timea”始于多次合作的惩罚游戏，但是当您重复数字时，您可以在互相战斗时一起笑，您可以一起笑。这是一种流行的组合，已经开始像即使在原始数量之后，也一直在协作。歌曲也反映了娱乐性的独特味道，只能给两个具有独特距离感的人，这也反映在歌曲中。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[#RobelNaitomea] 我们迎接 2024 年 [晚上 Robel/Kagura Mea]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wS28GE_Pvw0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>尽管即使您独自听这首歌也可以享受高质量，但如果您对通常的“ Robel Nomi Time”有所了解，这将更加愉快。</p><p>单击此处以获取过去的推荐文章：<br /><a href="https://www.moguravr.com/category/vtuber-weekly-infomation/">必看！推荐本周的Vtuber</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-weekly-23-1-21/">这段视频的帖子很棒！推荐本周的VTUBER视频（〜1月19日）</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
